OL,3,CHow close is Starmer to sacking
OL,4,Chimself?
OL,6,FOlly Robbins' testimony about how Lord
OL,7,FMandelson received vetting clearance
OL,8,Fto go to Washington as Britain's
OL,9,Fambassador is yet another blow to the
OL,10,Fperceived competence of the prime
OL,11,Fminister and his team.
OL,13,FThese are the headlines.
OL,15,F1) The Cabinet office did not
OL,16,Finitially believe Mandelson needed to
OL,17,Fbe vetted at all, but the foreign
OL,18,Foffice insisted;
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776819790
OL,3,CHow close is Starmer to sacking
OL,4,Chimself?
OL,6,F2) Downing Street put enormous
OL,7,Fpressure on the foreign office to rush
OL,8,Fthrough the vetting after the PM had
OL,9,Fannounced Mandelson would be the new
OL,10,Fambassador;
OL,12,F3) The foreign office's grant to
OL,13,FMandelson of developed vetting status
OL,14,Fwas in line with normal practice,
OL,15,Fthough Robbins believes the prime
OL,16,Fminister should never have announced
OL,17,FMandelson as ambassador;
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
