OL,3,CHow close is Starmer to sacking
OL,4,Chimself?
OL,6,FThat is damaging enough for Starmer,
OL,7,Fgiven that he was forced to sack
OL,8,FMandelson after only nine months when
OL,9,Femails leaked to Bloomberg proved that
OL,10,FMandelson's known friendship with
OL,11,FEpstein continued to be unhealthily
OL,12,Fclose after the late billionaire was
OL,13,Fjailed for paedophile crimes.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
