OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776819790
OL,3,CHow close is Starmer to sacking
OL,4,Chimself?
OL,6,FThe big mistake preceded Olly Robbins
OL,7,Feven taking up the job of permanent
OL,8,Funder-secretary at the foreign office.
OL,9,FThat was to announce Mandelson would
OL,10,Fbe US ambassador, with the King's
OL,11,Fofficial blessing.
OL,13,FStarmer did that, not Robbins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
